  "text": "Found 6 deprecated Java classes in the apache/flink repository under flink-streaming-java/src/. The main DataStream API deprecations include 3 classes:\n\n1. **AscendingTimestampExtractor** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java) - A timestamp extractor for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. No explicit replacement is noted in the deprecation javadoc, but it implements WatermarkStrategyWithPeriodicWatermarks<T>.\n\n2. **TextInputFormat** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java) - An input format for reading text files. Recommended replacement per deprecation notice: Use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink instead. This class should be removed if support for input/output formats in DataStream API is dropped.\n\n3. **TextOutputFormat** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java) - A file output format for writing objects to text files. Recommended replacement per deprecation notice: Use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink instead. This class should be removed if support for InputFormat and OutputFormat interfaces is dropped.\n\nAdditionally, 3 test harness classes in flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/ are deprecated:\n\n4. **StreamTaskTestHarness** (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/StreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Recommended replacement: StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\n5. **OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness** (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Recommended replacement: StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\n6. **TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness** (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Recommended replacement: StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\nThe deprecated I/O format classes (TextInputFormat and TextOutputFormat) are located in the legacy/io package and mark the transition away from the old input/output format API towards the newer FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink approach as part of FLIP-27 improvements."
}

